# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your Google OAuth Client ID to
# enable live syncing to Google Sheets. Restart the dev server after changing it.
#
# How to get one (free, ~5 min):
#   1. https://console.cloud.google.com  → create/select a project
#   2. APIs & Services → Library → enable "Google Sheets API"
#   3. APIs & Services → OAuth consent screen → set it up (External is fine),
#      add yourself as a Test user
#   4. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create Credentials → OAuth client ID
#      → Application type: Web application
#      → Authorized JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5173 (and 5174),
#        plus your production origin if you deploy
#   5. Copy the Client ID below.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
